latestIgtvVideos.title: BOL NA HALKE HALKE| KATHAK FUSION| DANCE COVER
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Today it's been an year when I posted my very first dance cover, the day I knew that dance is what makes me the happiest. I don't remember a day when I haven't danced since then.💗

These 365 days have been full of ups and downs, but at the end it was all worth it!✨
I stopped caring about what others think of me and starting doing things I enjoy the most doing. I have changed so much as a person, I have gained so much confidence, and I absolutely love this version of myself. I have learnt so much, I've seen myself grow. My terrace became my studio and my neighbours the audience lmao. 

I'm so grateful for everything! Today wherever I stand wouldn't have been possible without you guys. I want to thank each and every one of you for sticking around, for all the lovely messages I've recieved till date, for motivating me to do even better and for all the love you've given me!! Y'all have no idea how much that means to me!💗 
Here's to many more years🥂

Ps- Wanted this video to be a style I've never done before on this page, there are so many flaws in this video and I didn't mean to disrespect this dance form in any way.

Do you ever catch yourself stuck in negative self-talk?🫂

I know how hard it gets when your mind feels like a trap—when every thought feels loud and real. But not everything your brain tells you is the truth.
Sometimes, you have to hit pause and remind yourself: this isn’t the full picture. It’s not easy, and it doesn’t shift in a day—but slow, steady steps can change everything.❤️
